<note id="fs-idm198107264" class="os-teacher">
<title>Standards</title>
<para id="fs-idm243236768"><emphasis effect="bold">Topic</emphasis>: 8.6 Early Steps in the Civil Rights Movement (1940s and 1950s)</para>
