<para id="fs-idm481728944"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objective</emphasis>: Unit 8G Explain how and why the civil rights movements developed and expanded from 1945 to 1960</para>
<para id="fs-idm658774224"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Development</emphasis>: 8.2.I.B.i</para>
<para id="fs-idm472707712"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Thinking Skills</emphasis>: HTS-2 Sourcing and Situation, HTS-3 Source Claims and Evidence, HTS-4 Contextualization, HTS-5 Making Connections, HTS-6 Argumentation</para>
